import InputGroup from 'react-bootstrap/InputGroup';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import { Row,Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';

function Clients() {
  return (
    <>
    <Container>
      <Row>
        <Col lg={5}>
        <Form.Label htmlFor="CompanyName">Company Name:</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Name" id="CompanyName" />
        </Col>
      </Row>
    <Row className='my-5'>
      <Col lg={4}>
        
        <Form.Label htmlFor="Company Adresse">Company Adresse:</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" className='mb-2' id="Company Adresse" />
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
          <Row>
            <Col lg={4}>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
              </Col>
            <Col lg={4}>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
              </Col>
            <Col lg={4}>
              <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" id="Company Adresse" />
              </Col>
          </Row>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
        <Form.Label htmlFor="CompanyName">GST treatment</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
        <Form.Label htmlFor="CompanyName">VAT</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="Small text" />
      </Col>
      <Col lg={4}>
        <Form.Label htmlFor="Phone">Phone:</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Phone" />
        <Form.Label htmlFor="Phone">Phone:</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Phone" />
        <Form.Label htmlFor="Phone">Phone:</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Phone" />
        <Form.Label htmlFor="Phone">Phone:</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control size="sm" type="text" placeholder="2029311" id="Phone" />

      </Col>
      </Row>
      </Container>

    </>
  );
}

export default Clients;
